 || 🎨 Color Changing Mini Project ||

This is a simple and interactive **Color Changing** mini project built using **HTML**, **CSS**, and **JavaScript**. It allows users to change the background color of the webpage (or a specific element) either randomly or based on a selected color.

||  🚀 Features || 

- Change background color on button click
- Generate random colors
- Simple and clean UI
- Responsive layout (optional, if you added it)

|| 🛠️ Technologies Used ||

- **HTML5** – Markup structure
- **CSS3** – Styling and layout
- **JavaScript (ES6)** – Logic for color change and interactivity

 📂 Project Structure

||📸 Demo

|| 🧠 How It Works

1. The user clicks a button.
2. JavaScript generates a color (random or predefined).
3. The background color of the page or a section changes instantly.

